<li><a href="http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-65772" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-65772" rel="nofollow">Works by or about Athanasius Kircher</a> in libraries (<a href="/wiki/WorldCat" title="WorldCat">WorldCat</a> catalog)</li>
</ul>
